name: Laurie Lalla
text: Tried to order on line at the Mequon store, it would not work. I called and the owner answered, he took my order but would not give me the on line discount. He told me to find another coupon on line, I went in to pay and found a better …More

name: Sarah Lane
text: Shocked how amazing this pizza is. Highly recommend the pan dough. Pizza is so so yummy! Woman who works there during day is so kind and welcoming.

name: Chloe Mehall
text: Super friendly and helpful! Made my pizza in great time all while my son ran around their store! Definitely going back as the service is SO WONDERFUL!! Also it is very clean and staff was knowledgeable and clear.

name: goldenskin_ayla Luv
text: Pizza was great, but young female staff kept watching me as if I was going to steal from the tip money! She was pleasant, but when she walked away to get my salad items she kept looking suspiciously at me.

name: Tracy Switzer
text: Always so friendly and accommodating for whatever weird thing my family asks for on any given day. Today they are making a crustless pizza for us. The toppings are always so fresh and plentiful.

name: Tony Rambo
text: They accepted my expired coupons give them an extra star

name: ankur patel
text: Not a good crust,toppings were good

name: Sharon Karackattu
text: They don't honor their own advertisements!!!! I went in last week and attached to my pizza was was an ad saying they were doing $10 any pizza, any size on Tuesdays. Needing a quick, cheap and easy dinner on New Year's Day, I double checked …More

name: Noah Wolfgram
text: I love getting pizzas from this location. Always made fast and good when I'm there, and always ready if I call ahead of time.

name: Gary Rosenberg
text: Just posted a picture on Facebook (6/30/15) of a pathetic pepperoni pizza made in front of me by a bored teenager who probably didn't want to be working tonight --- my regular Papa Murphy's (77th & Good Hope) would be horrified to serve …More

name: brxdr
text:
Always happy with our product.
It  has been  our "go to" spot ever since we move to Mequon.

name: Ben Pinnow
text: Best pizza around always have sales! Also from the lady complaining businesses don't do specials on holidays they would lose all there money...

name: Brian Clendening
text: I really enjoy the pizza from here.
